arts.ttl: Richie Wellens rues lack of cutting edge as Leyton Orient held at home by Wigan
arts.sum: “They came for a point and in every single aspect of the game we was far better than them," said Wellens, "but the disappointment for us is we’ve had 16 shots and only three on target. “I thought our performance was good but we’ve got to be better in the final third.
